description: Castellum AB engages in the real estate business. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 413 full-time employees.  The firm is engaged in the acquisition, ownership, management and development of property on a long-term basis. The property portfolio of Castellum AB comprises commercial real estate, including offices, public sector properties, warehouses and logistics properties, retail properties and light industry properties, covering approximately 4.3 million square meters of total leasable area. The firm is also involved in the coworking and shared office space sector. Castellum AB operates in approximately 20 cities across Sweden, as well as in Copenhagen, Denmark and Helsinki, Finland.
name: Castellum AB
